Sunday, Wednesday, Friday, and Saturday of every week from 10 PM PT to 9:59 PM PT the next day<br>\\u30fbHigh Mercury&#39;s Trial: Master - Sunday, Tuesday, Friday, and Saturday of every week from 10 PM PT to 9:59 PM PT the next day<br>\\u30fbHigh Brunhilda&#39;s Trial: Master - Monday, Thursday, Friday, and Saturday of every week from 10 PM PT to 9:59 PM PT the next day<br>\\u30fbHigh Jupiter&#39;s Trial: Master - Tuesday, Thursday, Friday, and Saturday of every week from 10 PM PT to 9:59 PM PT the next day<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<br><br><\/div><hr><div>A new Expert difficulty was added to all Advanced Dragon Trials at <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1570773600\\"><\/span>!<\/div><div>Then, an even more challenging Master difficulty will be added on a rotating basis starting <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1571032800\\"><\/span>!<\/div><div>Additionally, a new set of high dragon weapons has been added for crafting!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/53a93677440ef70c9d113eb2a8012735.png\\"><\/div><div>Changes Accompanying the Addition of Expert and Master Difficulties<\/div><div>The naming for the current Advanced Dragon Trials quests, endeavors, and the conditions for obtaining the epithet will change as described below.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The quest name for each Advanced Dragon Trials quest will change as follows.<\/div><div>\\u30fbHigh Midgardsormr&#39;s Trial &rarr; High Midgardsormr&#39;s Trial: Standard<\/div><div>\\u30fbHigh Mercury&#39;s Trial &rarr; High Mercury&#39;s Trial: Standard<\/div><div>\\u30fbHigh Brunhilda&#39;s Trial &rarr; High Brunhilda&#39;s Trial: Standard<\/div><div>\\u30fbHigh Jupiter&#39;s Trial &rarr; High Jupiter&#39;s Trial: Standard<\/div><div>\\u30fbHigh Zodiark&#39;s Trial &rarr; High Zodiark&#39;s Trial: Standard<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Weekly Bonus<\/div><div>The weekly bonus for Advanced Dragon Trials also applies to Expert and Master difficulties.<\/div><div>The content of the weekly bonus differs depending on the difficulty.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Expert Difficulty Added<\/div><div>The following quests will be added <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1570773600\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div>\\u30fbHigh Midgardsormr&#39;s Trial: Expert<\/div><div>\\u30fbHigh Mercury&#39;s Trial: Expert<\/div><div>\\u30fbHigh Brunhilda&#39;s Trial: Expert<\/div><div>\\u30fbHigh Jupiter&#39;s Trial: Expert<\/div><div>\\u30fbHigh Zodiark&#39;s Trial: Expert<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Master Difficulty Added<\/div><div>The Master difficulty quest available for you to challenge will differ depending on the period.<\/div><div>The schedule for Master difficulty in Advanced Dragon Trials between <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1571032800\\"><\/span> and <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1574056799\\"><\/span> is as follows.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbHigh Brunhilda&#39;s Trial: Master<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1571032800\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1571637599\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbHigh Midgardsormr&#39;s Trial: Master<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1571637600\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1572242399\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbHigh Jupiter&#39;s Trial: Master<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1572242400\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1572847199\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbHigh Mercury&#39;s Trial: Master<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1572847200\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1573451999\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbHigh Zodiark&#39;s Trial: Master<\/div><div><span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1573452000\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1574056799\\"><\/span><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Then, from <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1574056800\\"><\/span> onwards, the schedule will be as follows.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbHigh Midgardsormr&#39;s Trial: Master - Sunday, Wednesday, Friday, and Saturday of every week from 10 PM PT to 9:59 PM PT the next day<br>\\u30fbHigh Mercury&#39;s Trial: Master - Sunday, Tuesday, Friday, and Saturday of every week from 10 PM PT to 9:59 PM PT the next day<br>\\u30fbHigh Brunhilda&#39;s Trial: Master - Monday, Thursday, Friday, and Saturday of every week from 10 PM PT to 9:59 PM PT the next day<br>\\u30fbHigh Jupiter&#39;s Trial: Master - Tuesday, Thursday, Friday, and Saturday of every week from 10 PM PT to 9:59 PM PT the next day<br>\\u30fbHigh Zodiark&#39;s Trial: Master - Monday, Wednesday, Friday, and Saturday of every week from 10 PM PT to 9:59 PM PT the next day<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0New High Dragon Weapons<br>A powerful new high dragon weapon set will be added for crafting starting at <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1570773600\\"><\/span>.<br>To craft weapons in the high dragon set, you must first obtain two other specific weapons.<br>The required weapons differ based on the weapon element and type for the weapon you wish to craft. You can check the requirements by first selecting Crafting on the Upgrade screen, then looking at the materials for each high dragon weapon on the Craft tab.<br>Note:High dragon weapons cannot be dismantled.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. In order to challenge Expert difficulty for each Advanced Dragon Trials quest, a player&#39;s team must have 20,000 might or higher.<\/div><div>2. In order to challenge Master difficulty for each Advanced Dragon Trials quest, a player&#39;s team must have 24,000 might or higher.<\/div><div>3. Players must have completed Standard difficulty for the corresponding Advanced Dragon Trials quest to challenge the Expert and Master difficulties.<\/div><div>Example: To challenge High Midgardsormr&#39;s Trial on Expert difficulty, players must clear High Midgardsormr&#39;s Trial on Standard difficulty.<\/div><div>4. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 \/ 2-1 (Normal) of the campaign in order to play co-op.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1570773600,"prev_article_id":"20001","next_article_id":"765","image_path":"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/53a93677440ef70c9d113eb2a8012735.png","update_time":1573813433}}}'